ul.li:
Show all components - Displays all the components that were
        collected starting from current document or from the main document in case it is
        defined;

body.note:
The search filter is case insensitive. The following wildcards are accepted:

* - any string;

? - any character;

, - patterns separator.
      If no wildcards are specified, the string to search is used as a partial match (like
        *textToFind*).
